# Session — 2026-07-15

## Goal for today
Move from planning into building. Get the ESP32 toolchain working, prove each
subsystem in isolation, and start on the display.

## What I did
- Installed PlatformIO in VS Code and created the firmware project inside the repo.
- Wrote a blink program to verify the whole toolchain (compile → link → flash → run).
- Fixed a driver problem preventing upload (see Problems).
- Added serial output with an uptime counter — this is now my main debugging tool.
- Wired the OLED over I2C and confirmed the bus with an address scanner (found 0x3C).
- Displayed text on the OLED using the Adafruit SSD1306 + GFX libraries.
